{"tid":772348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國遊客抵制泰國，退訂酒店房間，泰國人：過段時間又來了","createTime":"2018-08-08T16:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T18:18:09.000Z","uid":1221,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9d78ee1890648a73a1cb2764e24dfe889ec8a028","tid":772348,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"近年泰國在國內可以說是相當火爆，每年赴泰的中國遊客都在上漲，可是今年泰國卻事故頻出，負面消息不斷，對泰國旅遊業造成了很大的影響。之前的假笑迎賓女孩和泰國黑心導遊的熱度剛剛，隨後普吉島就發生了一件令國人傷心的事情，普吉島的乘船事故死傷眾多，同時泰國給的官方回應更是讓不少中國遊客感到心寒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img3.guangsuss.com/4a80946a517bf0a92c65d2b8d83fb99b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.guangsuss.com%2F4a80946a517bf0a92c65d2b8d83fb99b&h=235d97a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國官方回應此次事故皆由中國遊客引起，是中國遊客不聽勸阻非要出海導致，所以中國遊客自己負責。可是據有關知情人士透露，當天出海前，碼頭並未有任何警示，而且掛的還是綠色安全旗，表示是可以出海的，當時船隻是上午出海，等到下午的時候天氣驟變發生了現在的悲劇，而根據目擊者爆料，泰國政府等部門也是在當天下午變天之前才在碼頭掛出警示，而那個時候已經晚了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img3.guangsuss.com/8f36878ce3f93e902e1af63257f3093e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.guangsuss.com%2F8f36878ce3f93e902e1af63257f3093e&h=8cd655ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事故發生及時處理好，做好後續的工作才是正確的，可是讓中國人寒心的不是去泰​​國旅遊出了事故不作為，而是泰國在不作為之後給出的一系列詭辯，他們的反應太讓中國遊客失望了，於是隨後<span style=\"color: red;\">中國遊客就取消了在泰國普吉島的7300家訂房</span>，使得泰國酒店業損失慘重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.travelliker.com.hk/img/upload/post-banner/13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelliker.com.hk%2Fimg%2Fupload%2Fpost-banner%2F13.jpg&h=086b5e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看到中國遊客終於還是做出了反擊，退訂了房間後，泰國官方也給出回應， 為之前的言論來道歉，可是潑出去的水哪有收回來的到底，還是造成了影響，赴泰旅遊的人數也在不斷下滑。不過也有泰國人表示：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>不用擔心，中國人果斷時間又回來了，他們抵制不了多久的。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6058cb0b68d4ac7187eb88b48cd8d6a5a57d32b2","tid":772348,"uid":191405,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:27:16.000Z","msg":"有遠見啊 <br />\n次次都係抵制一排<br />\n轉個頭咩事都無咁 照去幫襯"},{"pid":"95c812ddb9e22267863c0524326bafae7bcbcf6a","tid":772348,"uid":8858,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"中國抵制天大笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560b38e4426b4c14df2267b416457c41abb0a334","tid":772348,"uid":114483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"中國人=反口覆舌<br />\n香港、日本、韓國咪又係一車車送過去"},{"pid":"254266efa72b3d1938a42a5a6d29794dbf020d07","tid":772348,"uid":19872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"可以去泰國旅行了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd65c66793ae31a7d2bf742a7e1181c2be0167ff","tid":772348,"uid":960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"還泰國淨土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係先王庇佑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfafae850bb4fbb758a27bb9b3906f8f29781a2","tid":772348,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實應該抵制美帝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f49efd91bca8ac24292b6bb65d5c5dddc2f89a6","tid":772348,"uid":100276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"班支那蟲係屌極都唔走，可參考旺角"},{"pid":"f10e4cbeda3168ae6d28f9e80c22e5bbc5903533","tid":772348,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:53:49.000Z","msg":"成七億隻蝗, 驚閪咩"},{"pid":"051390befe955341edcf0f2228efc4bc84bba1d2","tid":772348,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"